        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 cursor-pointer hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" id="revolutionary-title">
          Why Our Master Assessment is
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all duration-500">
            Revolutionary
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
          While others force you through multiple forms and outdated systems, we've built something that changes everything.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- ImmiReport Standard -->
        <div class="feature-card bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-blue-800/20 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 cursor-pointer transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 group" data-feature="immi-report">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-500">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
