          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 group-hover:text-gray-800 dark:group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">Our algorithm has the complete NOC system embedded, automatically matching your experience with the most appropriate occupational codes for maximum scoring.</p>
